== 開發 ==
遊戲開發於2010年1月展開，由育碧軟件一隊資深開發團隊<ref name="gi1">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/03/01/april-cover-revealed-assassin-39-s-creed-iii.aspx|title=April Cover Revealed: Assassin's Creed III|last=Miller|first=Matt|date=2012-03-01|publisher=''[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]''|accessdate=2012-03-01|archive-date=2017-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171105105324/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/03/01/april-cover-revealed-assassin-39-s-creed-iii.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>以兩年半時間製作，是自《[[刺客教條_(遊戲)|刺客教條]]》以來開發周期最長的作品<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nowgamer.com/features/1326914/assassins_creed_3_why_starting_from_scratch_has_been_worth_it_interview.html |title=Assassin’s Creed 3: Why Starting From Scratch Has Been Worth It – Interview (Feature) |publisher=NowGamer |date=2012-04-18 |accessdate=2012-07-28 |archive-date=2012-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609125444/http://www.nowgamer.com/features/1326914/assassins_creed_3_why_starting_from_scratch_has_been_worth_it_interview.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kotaku.com/5896386/50-things-about-assassins-creed-iii-that-you-should-know |title=50 Things About Assassin’s Creed III That You Should Know |publisher=Kotaku |date=2012-03-26 |accessdate=2012-07-28 |archive-date=2012-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120806064111/http://kotaku.com/5896386/50-things-about-assassins-creed-iii-that-you-should-know |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部分遊戲團體在育碧軟件於2010年首次公開《[[刺客教條：兄弟會|刺客教條：兄弟會]]》時誤以為它是《刺客教條III》，開發人員作出澄清並表示第三部主要作品不會以現有角色作為主角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ps3blog.net/2010/07/08/assassins-creed-brotherhood-is-not-assassins-creed-3|title=Assassin’s Creed: Brotherhood is not Assassin’s Creed 3|accessdate=2015-01-23|archive-date=2012-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120303230650/http://www.ps3blog.net/2010/07/08/assassins-creed-brotherhood-is-not-assassins-creed-3/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.neoseeker.com/news/14389-ubisoft-brotherhood-is-not-assassins-creed-25/ |title=Ubisoft: Brotherhood is not Assassin's Creed 2.5 – Neoseeker News Article |publisher=Neoseeker.com |date=2010-07-20 |accessdate=2012-03-01 |archive-date=2012-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304010019/http://www.neoseeker.com/news/14389-ubisoft-brotherhood-is-not-assassins-creed-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，系列內每部名稱含有數字的作品皆有新主角與新背景設定<ref name="ac3-gamerzine">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerzines.com/ps3/news/assassins-creed-3-details.html|title=Ubisoft reveals first ever details on Assassin's Creed 3|publisher=Gamerzines.com|date=2010-06-08|accessdate=2010-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100822001845/http://www.gamerzines.com/ps3/news/assassins-creed-3-details.html|archive-date=2010-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。刺客教條系列前創意總監派崔斯·德斯里斯（Patrice Désilets）表示系列一直以來均以三部曲開發，《刺客教條III》將以刺客阻止2012年世界末日和尋找第一文明密室與伊甸碎片作為核心，現代刺客主角戴斯蒙將透過搜索祖先記憶獲得密室位置的線索<ref name="ac-vgb-ultimate">{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamesblogger.com/2009/06/10/assassins-creed-3-will-see-desmond-become-the-ultimate-assassin.htm|title=Assassins Creed 3 will see Desmond Miles become the Ultimate Assassin|publisher=Video Games Blogger|date=2009-06-10|accessdate=2010-11-17|archive-date=2011-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717200033/http://www.videogamesblogger.com/2009/06/10/assassins-creed-3-will-see-desmond-become-the-ultimate-assassin.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[刺客教條：啟示錄|刺客教條：啟示錄]]》創意總監阿歷山杜·阿曼西奧（Alexandre Amacio）於2011年10月宣佈系列新作將於2012年12月前推出，但他不會監督遊戲開發<ref name="amancioquit">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamingunion.net/news/assassins-creed-revelations-creative-director-quits-ubisoft--7488.html|title=Assassin's Creed: Revelations Creative Director Quits Ubisoft|publisher=GamingUnion.net|date=2012-01-11|accessdate=2011-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113200536/http://www.gamingunion.net/news/assassins-creed-revelations-creative-director-quits-ubisoft--7488.html|archive-date=2012-01-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，也表示新作品的時代結束後將不會有包含未來色彩的遊戲<ref>{{cite web|last=Pereira|first=Chris|title=Expect a Larger Gap Between Future Assassin's Creed Releases|url=http://www.1up.com/news/expect-larger-gap-between-assassins-creed-games|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|accessdate=2015-01-23|archive-date=2012-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622060907/http://www.1up.com/news/expect-larger-gap-between-assassins-creed-games|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

育碧軟件行政總裁伊域斯·吉利莫特（Yves Guillemot）於2011年11月8日確認新的刺客教條主作會於2012年推出，但拒絕透露更多詳情<ref>{{cite web|last=Jackson|first=Mike|title=New Assassin's Creed in 2012, confirms Ubi|url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/325502/new-assassins-creed-in-2012-confirms-ubi/|publisher=''[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]''|accessdate=2015-01-23|archive-date=2012-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107191851/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/325502/new-assassins-creed-in-2012-confirms-ubi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時指出每年推出刺客教條遊戲的目的是滿足需求並否認此舉將導致系列質素下降，而且該年度的作品將是系列一直以來的最大一作<ref>{{cite web |author=Robinson, Andy |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/333495/assassins-creed-3-will-be-series-biggest-yet-ubisoft/ |title=Assassin's Creed 3 will be series' 'biggest yet' – Ubisoft |publisher=''[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]'' |date=2012-01-26 |accessdate=2012-03-01 |archive-date=2012-02-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229191322/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/333495/assassins-creed-3-will-be-series-biggest-yet-ubisoft/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。肓碧軟件於2012年2月正式證實《刺客教條III》存在，北美首發日期為2012年10月30日<ref name="AC3-conf">{{cite web|last=Reilly|first=Jim|title=Assassin's Creed III Coming In October|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/02/15/assassin-39-s-creed-3-release-date.aspx|accessdate=2012-12-27|publisher=''[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]''|date=2012-02-15|archive-date=2012-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121215024827/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/02/15/assassin-39-s-creed-3-release-date.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。吉利莫特形容遊戲為刺客教條系列及互動娛樂的真正次世代作品，團隊開發了三年因此也使遊戲進步了不少<ref name="AC3-conf"/><ref name="AC3-confirmed"/>，更指遊戲所獲投資高於系列過往任何一作<ref name="AC3-confirmed">{{cite web |author=Ivan, Tom |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/336082/assassins-creed-3-release-date-october-30/ |title=Assassin's Creed 3 release confirmed for October |publisher=''[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]'' |date=2012-02-15 |accessdate=2012-03-01 |archive-date=2012-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120220190122/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/336082/assassins-creed-3-release-date-october-30/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

育碧軟件內部消息被指於2012年1月透露了遊戲時代定於美國革命時期<ref>{{cite web |author=Robinson, Andy |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/333754/assassins-creed-3-heads-to-american-revolution-rumour/?cid=OTC-RSS&attr=CVG-General-RSS |title=Assassin's Creed 3 heads to American Revolution – Rumour |publisher=''[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]]'' |date=2012-01-27 |accessdate=2012-03-01 |archive-date=2012-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219090416/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/333754/assassins-creed-3-heads-to-american-revolution-rumour/?cid=OTC-RSS&attr=CVG-General-RSS |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同年2月29日一幅未公開宣傳圖像和它即將被公開的消息被傳送至[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]<ref name="EG-leak">{{cite web |last=Phillips |first=Tom |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-03-01-assassins-creed-3-set-in-american-revolution-report |title=Assassin's Creed 3 set in American Revolution – report |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date= |accessdate=2012-03-01 |archive-date=2012-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120303160422/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-03-01-assassins-creed-3-set-in-american-revolution-report |dead-url=no }}</ref>，使外部一致認為遊戲將定於美國革命時期的北美洲或是一個寒冷下雪的時期<ref>{{cite web|url=http://oxcgn.com/2012/03/01/assassins-creed-3-oxcgn-picks-american-revolution-in-march-2011-evidence-now-in/|title=Assassin's Creed 3: OXCGN Picks American Revolution in March 2011 – Evidence now in!|last=Laborde|first=Nicholas|date=2012-03-01|publisher=OXCGN|accessdate=2012-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120303151721/http://oxcgn.com/2012/03/01/assassins-creed-3-oxcgn-picks-american-revolution-in-march-2011-evidence-now-in/|archive-date=2012-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。育碧軟件於約莫同一時期在其官方[[Facebook|Facebook]]帳戶提及一項刺客教條重要消息即將公佈，帳戶的封面圖片亦有雪景<ref name="EG-leak"/>，[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]也透過其官方網頁公開新刺客主角與美國革命領袖一起的圖片。<ref name="EG-leak"/>

育碧軟件於2012年11月14日表示遊戲的個人電腦版本的bug數量將比PlayStation 3及Xbox 360版本少，以及會為遊戲所有版本發行[[補丁|補丁]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Phillips |first=Tom |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-11-14-assassins-creed-3-pc-will-be-less-buggy-than-the-console-versions-at-launch |title=Assassin's Creed 3 PC "will be less buggy than the console versions" at launch |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2012-11-14 |accessdate=2012-11-28 |archive-date=2012-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121117093459/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-11-14-assassins-creed-3-pc-will-be-less-buggy-than-the-console-versions-at-launch |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11月16日，育碧軟件列出補丁的內容，針對多達一百項已確定的單人任務和線上多人模式bug，包括環境不穩定、非玩家角色技術故障、主機系統癱瘓及角色聲唇不吻合等<ref>{{cite web |last=Phillips |first=Tom |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-11-16-huge-assassins-creed-3-patch-detailed |title=Ubisoft details huge Assassin's Creed 3 patch |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2012-11-16 |accessdate=2012-11-28 |archive-date=2012-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121130085608/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-11-16-huge-assassins-creed-3-patch-detailed |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2017年9月12日，育碧宣布为《刺客信条3》加入了简体中文的语言选项。<ref>[https://weibo.com/1928890987/FltUIiVCo @育碧中国: 育碧“官方中文回归计划”新游戏作品-《#刺客信条3# 》简体中文版正式推出！].新浪微博.2017-09-12.[2017-09-12].</ref>

== 行銷 ==
2012年3月30日，育碧軟件表示遊戲自接受預訂起至三個星期後，預訂數量已超越《刺客教條：兄弟會》的全美國預購量及超越《刺客教條：啟示錄》預購量的十倍<ref name=AC3-preorder>{{cite web |author=PDT |url=http://asia.gamespot.com/news/assassins-creed-iii-setting-ubisoft-preorder-records-6368828 |title=Assassin's Creed III setting Ubisoft preorder records — GameSpot.com |publisher=[[Gamespot|Gamespot]] |date=2012-03-29 |accessdate=2012-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120401234257/http://asia.gamespot.com/news/assassins-creed-iii-setting-ubisoft-preorder-records-6368828 |archive-date=2012-04-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2012年10月25日，育碧軟件宣佈遊戲預訂數量創下紀錄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/10/25/assassins-creed-iii-pre-orders-break-ubisoft-record?abthid=50896fcbf6090bd57d000033|title=Assassin’s Creed III Pre-Orders Break Ubisoft Record|last=Goldfarb|first=Andrew|date=2012-10-25|accessdate=2012-10-25|publisher=IGN|archive-date=2012-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121030022002/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/10/25/assassins-creed-iii-pre-orders-break-ubisoft-record?abthid=50896fcbf6090bd57d000033|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

遊戲在英國發行首星期時排行第一，是育碧軟件有史以來發行表現最理想的遊戲，於英國2012年間發行表現排行第三（落後於《[[使命召喚：黑色行動II|使命召喚：黑色行動II]]》和《[[FIFA_13|FIFA 13]]》）；於北美2012年銷情排行第四<ref name="Salesof2012">{{cite web| first=Jordan| last=Mallory| url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/01/10/december-npd-2012-sales-hit-13-26-billion-black-ops-2-leads-t/| title=December NPD: 2012 sales hit $13.26 billion, Black Ops 2 leads the pack| publisher=AOL| work=Joystiq| date=2013-01-10| accessdate=2013-01-11| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Da2gjZ6A?url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/01/10/december-npd-2012-sales-hit-13-26-billion-black-ops-2-leads-t/| archivedate=2013-01-11| deadurl=yes}}</ref>。遊戲首星期銷售數量是《刺客教條II》的兩倍也比《啟示錄》多售約117,000份<ref>{{cite web |last=Phillips |first=Tom |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-11-05-uk-charts-assassins-creed-3-top-second-biggest-launch-of-the-year |title=UK chart: Assassin's Creed 3 top, second biggest launch of the year |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2012-11-05 |accessdate=2012-11-09 |archive-date=2012-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108001645/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-11-05-uk-charts-assassins-creed-3-top-second-biggest-launch-of-the-year |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2222373/assassin-s-creed-3-making-a-killing-in-the-uk-games-charts|title=AC3 Sales|publisher=The Inquirer|accessdate=2012-11-05|archive-date=2012-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108044116/http://www.theinquirer.net/inquirer/news/2222373/assassin-s-creed-3-making-a-killing-in-the-uk-games-charts|dead-url=no}}</ref>，育碧軟件的數量顯示遊戲於發售首星期售出超過三百五十萬份<ref>{{cite web |last=Matulef |first=Jeffrey |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-11-06-assassins-creed-3-sales-estimated-at-over-3-5-million-units |title=Assassin's Creed 3 sales estimated at over 3.5 million units |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2012-11-06 |accessdate=2012-11-28 |archive-date=2012-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121211071645/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-11-06-assassins-creed-3-sales-estimated-at-over-3-5-million-units |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年12月12日，育碧宣佈遊戲於全球售出七百萬份<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/12/12/assassins-creed-iii-sales-pass-7-million |title=Assassin’s Creed III Sales Pass 7 Million |publisher=IGN |date= |accessdate=2012-12-22 |archive-date=2012-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121214202928/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/12/12/assassins-creed-iii-sales-pass-7-million |dead-url=no }}</ref>，於2013年2月7日時已於全球售出一千二百萬份，是《啟示錄》生命週期同一時段大約1.7倍<ref>{{cite web |last=Ivan |first=Tom |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/389939/assassins-creed-3-12-million-sales-boost-ubisofts-q3/ |title=News: Assassin's Creed 3: 12 million sales boost Ubisoft's Q3 |publisher=ComputerAndVideoGames.com |date=2013-02-07 |accessdate=2013-02-21 |archive-date=2013-02-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130212100825/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/389939/assassins-creed-3-12-million-sales-boost-ubisofts-q3/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

